      • getMementoCreatedDate

        Instant getMementoCreatedDate()
        Get the date a memento for this resource was created. This field should generally be kept in sync with the last modified date, but they may not be the same, in the case that a memento was created as a result of an update to a different resource. Additionally, this date is NOT the same as the actual memento timestamp, which is determined by the timestamp on the OCFL version.
        Returns:
        memento created date
